{"version":1,"name":"매듭의 길","blueprints":[{"id":1,"title":"굽이 1","objectLabel":"","emoji":"·","position":[-0.61,0,-0.0],"scale":1,"hue":"#eee5d3","objectKit":"none","pathKind":"meadow","surface":"moss-aged","weather":"clear","cameraShot":"side","importance":1,"stillness":0.35,"soundTone":174,"text":"길이 길 위를\n지나간다.\n누구의 발소리가\n위였을까."},{"id":2,"title":"굽이 2","objectLabel":"","emoji":"·","position":[-0.36,0,-2.8],"scale":1,"hue":"#eee5d3","objectKit":"none","pathKind":"meadow","surface":"moss-aged","weather":"clear","cameraShot":"side","importance":1,"stillness":0.35,"soundTone":174,"text":"아까 걸었던 길이\n머리 위로\n흘러간다."},{"id":3,"title":"굽이 3","objectLabel":"","emoji":"·","position":[-0.61,0,-5.6],"scale":1,"hue":"#eee5d3","objectKit":"none","pathKind":"meadow","surface":"moss-aged","weather":"clear","cameraShot":"side","importance":1,"stillness":0.35,"soundTone":174,"text":"올라가는 길과\n내려가는 길이\n결국\n한 길이다."},{"id":4,"title":"굽이 4","objectLabel":"","emoji":"·","position":[-0.12,0,-8.4],"scale":1,"hue":"#eee5d3","objectKit":"none","pathKind":"meadow","surface":"moss-aged","weather":"clear","cameraShot":"side","importance":1,"stillness":0.35,"soundTone":174,"text":"다리 밑을 지날 때\n잠깐\n어두워졌다가\n다시 환해진다."},{"id":5,"title":"굽이 5","objectLabel":"","emoji":"·","position":[0.75,0,-11.2],"scale":1,"hue":"#eee5d3","objectKit":"none","pathKind":"meadow","surface":"moss-aged","weather":"clear","cameraShot":"side","importance":1,"stillness":0.35,"soundTone":174,"text":"매듭은\n풀라고 있는 게 아니라\n걸으라고 있다."},{"id":6,"title":"굽이 6","objectLabel":"","emoji":"·","position":[0.97,0,-14.0],"scale":1,"hue":"#eee5d3","objectKit":"none","pathKind":"meadow","surface":"moss-aged","weather":"clear","cameraShot":"side","importance":1,"stillness":0.35,"soundTone":174,"text":"세 번 겹치고\n세 번 풀리는\n길."},{"id":7,"title":"굽이 7","objectLabel":"","emoji":"·","position":[1.11,0,-16.8],"scale":1,"hue":"#eee5d3","objectKit":"none","pathKind":"meadow","surface":"moss-aged","weather":"clear","cameraShot":"side","importance":1,"stilln